				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Gale is a Companion.\r\nThis dialogue can trigger as COM (if the players approach Elminster with Gale as a companion), as a regular dialogue (if the players approach Elminster while Companion Gale is in the camp) or a CFM (if the player skips Elminster altogether).\r\nIt can trigger in either Creche or SCL."
